232
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:58,279
Yiyang.

233
00:20:58,279 --> 00:20:59,559
Yiyang.

234
00:20:59,559 --> 00:21:00,400
Let him go.

235
00:21:07,519 --> 00:21:11,080
Lin Yiyang.

236
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:16,600
Who doesn't make mistakes?
Can't you apologize?

237
00:21:18,840 --> 00:21:22,400
