257
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:55,279
It's okay. Anyway,
I have to face them eventually.

258
00:23:56,680 --> 00:23:58,440
You have a good mind.

259
00:24:00,039 --> 00:24:01,719
If the goal is the championship,

260
00:24:02,239 --> 00:24:04,640
