262
00:24:17,080 --> 00:24:18,160
I want to practice.

263
00:24:20,279 --> 00:24:23,120
Okay, be careful.

264
00:24:23,640 --> 00:24:25,160
I just saw the team doctor today.

265
00:24:25,160 --> 00:24:26,719
