267
00:24:28,840 --> 00:24:30,279
Alright, I got it.

268
00:24:30,279 --> 00:24:30,888
Okay.

269
00:24:31,959 --> 00:24:32,519
I'm off.

270
00:24:32,519 --> 00:24:34,160
